Job Details:
Team Leader :
Responsibilities
- Communicate with PM/report project status;
- Actively cooperate with PM requirements, promote and implement project plans;
- Responsible for the project progress management, quality control and problem solving of your own team;
- Guide and help solve technical problems on the project;
- Manage the daily duties and work tasks of your own team;
- Promote team building and new employee training;

Team Leader :
Requirements
- Bachelor degree or above;
- Proficient in at least one mainstream technology of ERP (SAP/Oracle, etc.) or system integration (Java/.net/C++, Python, etc.);
- 5 years or more of development or operation and design experience;
- Fluent in English, Korean is a bonus
- Have good language expression skills, and communication and coordination skills with superiors and subordinates;
- Have strong execution ability;

Developer and operation:
Responsibilities
- Complete the development and testing or operation tasks undertaken according to the progress and process
- Actively report to superiors, communicate project status, and actively learn project knowledge
- Complete various project documents and reports as required
- Help and guide newcomers to quickly integrate into the team

Developer and operation :
Requirements
- Bachelor degree or above;
- Proficient in at least one mainstream ERP (SAP/Oracle, etc.) or system integration (Java/.net/C ++, Python, etc.) technology;
- 3 years or more of development or operation and maintenance experience, good programming skills and habits;
- Can communicate in English, Korean is a bonus
- Have good learning ability and strong sense of responsibility
